  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0b93\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Peaceful protest for burial site in Nanu'oya Krimiti",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "People on Sunday (03) staged a peaceful protest demanding a place for cremation at Nanuoa Krimiti.",
        "An individual has usurped the place reserved for burying the bodies of the dead soldiers for more than 8 years in the Nanuyoya Krimitia area and built a new house there and got electricity.",
        "In protest against this, a protest was carried out in the main town of Girimitti on the Nuwara Eliya-Talawagkalai main road.",
        "The protest was carried out demanding that the place be provided for the burial of the bodies and insisting that the police should conduct a proper investigation."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Nanu'oya",
          "label": "CARDINAL"
        },
